containing an area of TWO MILLION NINE HUNDRED TWENTY ONE THOUSAND FOUR HUNDRED AND NINETEEN (2,921,419) SQUARE METERS, more or less.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan and marked on the ground as follows: points 2, 5, 6 by x on tree and the rest P.S. Cyl . Conc . Mons. 15 x 50 cm.

This lot was surveyed by Wilfrido P. Ligutom , Geodetic Engineer, on November 15, 2001 and was approved on May 20, 2002 in accordance with law and existing regulations promulgated.

This proclamation shall be deemed automatically revoked or cancelled in the event that the reservation no longer serves the purpose for which it was originally established and/or has been abandoned by the reservee and the area covered thereby be forthwith reverted to the mass of forestland under the administrative jurisdiction of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources through its appropriate agency.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done, in the City of Manila this 26th day of November in the year of our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

( Sgd .) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: ( Sgd .) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

